                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030216-90-off478 t18030216-90-cd479"></join>, two sheets, value 8s. a counterpane, value 6s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18030216-90-victim631" type="victimName">
