                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030216-90-defend629 t18030216-90-punish482"></join>
               Whipped in the jail
            </rs> and discharged.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
